text: a user is enrolling to ScoreSense

results.text: Assuming that a user has never previously enrolled
And a user has completed Enrollment Enrollment
Given a user is on the New Member Page
When they submit a blank form
Then it should stay on the New Member Page
And the user name should be required
And the password should be required
And the answer should be required
And the date of birth should be required
And the social security number should be required
Given a user is on the New Member Page
When they enter a user name less than 6 characters
Then it should stay on the New Member Page
And it should say the user name is invalid
Given a user is on the New Member Page
When the user name is all repeating numbers
Then it should stay on the New Member Page
And it should say the user name is invalid
Given a user is on the New Member Page
When the password is less than 6 characters
Then it should stay on the New Member Page
And it should say the password is invalid
Given a user is on the New Member Page
When the password is all alpha characters
Then it should stay on the New Member Page
And it should say the password is invalid
Given a user is on the New Member Page
When the password is all numbers
Then it should stay on the New Member Page
And it should say the password is invalid
Given a user is on the New Member Page
When the passwords do not match
Then it should stay on the New Member Page
And it should say the password do not match
Given a user is on the New Member Page
When the date of birth is pre-1900
Then it should stay on the New Member Page
And it should say the date of birth is invalid
Given a user is on the New Member Page
When the date of birth is invalid
Then it should stay on the New Member Page
And it should say the date of birth is invalid
Given a user is on the New Member Page
When the social security numbers do not match
Then it should stay on the New Member Page
And it should say the date of birth is invalid
Given a user is on the New Member Page
When the form is completed
Then it should redirect to L3
